<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Spright" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Spright</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Sprite,</orth> == spirit; 1) mood, occasional state of the mind: <cit><quote>with a lazy s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 181" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 181</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>intending weariness with heavy s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 121" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 121</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>cheer we up his --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 1, 127</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) mind, soul: <cit><quote>her winged s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1728" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1728</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the quintessence of every s. heaven would in little show,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.147" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 147</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 56</bibl> (Ff <emph>spirit</emph>).
<lb />3) any supernatural being: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.381" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 381</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.121" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.192" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 192</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.400.33" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 400</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 26</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.5.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 5, 27</bibl>. == ghost: <bibl n="shak. luc 451" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 451</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.388" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 388</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 34</bibl> (Q <emph>spirit</emph>). <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 84</bibl>.
